{"tid":1026083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"體通天下擸兩季英足盃直播權 車仔曼聯大戰有得免費睇","createTime":"2019-02-17T23:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T15:52:46.000Z","uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9507c4c1df1cd738b1a2efc0a6901b4636be1dd2","tid":1026083,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:23:50.000Z","msg":"獲得今季NBA網絡播映權的網絡媒體《體通天下》，周一宣佈獲得2018至2020年連續兩季英格蘭足總盃、德國甲組聯賽、荷蘭甲組聯賽以及19至20球季的中國超級聯賽播映權。值得留意的是，《體通天下》亦會免費直播周二深夜英足盃第五圈，車路士主場對曼聯的重點賽事。<br />\n<br />\n如要收看曼聯對車路士的大戰，球迷需要下載《體通天下》的手機程式，之後登記成為會員即可。<br />\n<br />\n英足盃第五圈免費直播賽事<br />\n日期<br />\n時間<br />\n對賽<br />\n19-2-2019<br />\n0330<br />\n車路士 對 曼聯"},{"pid":"5edc6d51f709b3172cf5d57e782ab55f2bfda8e6","tid":1026083,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4710bdcb267f942e239789f640facf094f3501","tid":1026083,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"唔撚洗瞓咩"},{"pid":"77ae305cdf74aaf74e210c086df179c12fcbffb2","tid":1026083,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T03:19:14.000Z","msg":"CCCCC"},{"pid":"4f98aed9c9fac14e1b0fc4c9cbf5c645acf74475","tid":1026083,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}